---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About"
  description="[PLACEHOLDER: About page for an engineering portfolio.]"
>
  <section class="mx-auto grid max-w-6xl gap-10 px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:grid-cols-[0.8fr_1.2fr] lg:px-8">
    <div>
      <p class="font-mono text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-teal-200">About</p>
      <h1 class="mt-4 text-4xl font-semibold text-white sm:text-5xl">[PLACEHOLDER: Builder, debugger, systems thinker.]</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="space-y-6 text-base leading-8 text-zinc-300">
      <p>[PLACEHOLDER: Tell the story of how you got into engineering. Keep it specific: a class, a club, a hard project, a test stand, a production bug, or a problem that changed how you work.]</p>
      <p>[PLACEHOLDER: Explain what you are strongest at today. Mention concrete tools, domains, and the type of team environment where you do your best work.]</p>
      <p>[PLACEHOLDER: Add a human note: what you are learning now, what you read, what you build outside class, or what kind of problems make you lose track of time.]</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="border-y border-white/10 bg-zinc-900/40">
    <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-6xl gap-5 px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 md:grid-cols-3 lg:px-8">
      <div>
        <p class="font-mono text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-amber-300">Focus</p>
        <p class="mt-3 text-zinc-300">[PLACEHOLDER: Backend systems, embedded tooling, simulation, or aerospace software.]</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="font-mono text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-amber-300">Workflow</p>
        <p class="mt-3 text-zinc-300">[PLACEHOLDER: Testable interfaces, clear docs, reproducible builds, and measured tradeoffs.]</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="font-mono text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-amber-300">Current</p>
        <p class="mt-3 text-zinc-300">[PLACEHOLDER: Replace with what you are studying, prototyping, or shipping this semester.]</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
